March 12th 35
Dearest Enid:
Yes dearie send Hilda you know suit and the pink dress - Am glad you can use the other things - You must not even think of sending me a suit precious girlie mine - I'll get any thing I want or need you may be sure of that. You are very fortunate to have your job and Amama and you must please not misunderstand my attitude. I am so grateful you are where you are and have what you have - but I feel your experience has been for ma-nuscript work and that you might be transferred to such a position - where most 

