Daddy was all shot - but he is a great deal better now and loads well too.
I am getting fat! I eat a lot and have not had a real head ache for almost 4 months. 
Hilda wrote a dandy letter not-long ago - I am so grateful she is well and so enthusiastic over her studies. 
Yes dear we will do as we said about Omaha - I feel that will work out if you want it to. 
Loads of Love to you and to my own dearest Mommie as well 
from 
